snippet.title: Soulfire: a competitive multiplayer game focused on medieval weapons
snippet.description:
Soulfire is a tactical competitive game, only one person can survive from a hundred-people war.Compared to similar games, it features a melee-focused action system.
Steam:  http://store.steampowered.com/app/822800/Soulfire
Official website:  http://www.aydream.com
